## Introduction
Your portfolio is your calling card. Data science is a competitive field, and standing out to potential employers is important. 
Your portfolio showcases your academic journey and accomplishments and helps you land your dream job. 
This blog post will guide you through the essential steps to create a compelling data science portfolio to showcase your skills and impress potential employers.

